{"data": [{"id": "4745754", "title": "Joey Politano On The AI Investment Boom And Trends In Economic Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cloud computing, NFT, AI, artificial intelligence\" data-id=\"1336131137\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">blackdovfx</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Joey Politano is an economist and a commentator who writes a popular Substack newsletter on economics. Joey is also a returning guest to Macro Musings, and he rejoins David to talk about the AI investment boom and broader economic growth trends. Specifically, David</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745754-joey-politano-ai-investment-boom-trends-economic-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 10:20:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745752", "title": "Lazard International Equity Select Portfolio Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial charts\" data-id=\"172483014\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vertigo3d</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Market Overview</h2> <ul> <li> International markets were strong during the quarter adding to gains for the past year</li> <li>Despite concerns about slowing economic growth, earnings estimates have proven resilient and continue to rise</li> <li>Chinese coordinated monetary stimulus drove stocks</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172483014/image_172483014.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745752-lazard-international-equity-select-portfolio-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 10:15:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745751", "title": "Sovereign Funds Pull Back On Transactions; Financial Media Deal Value Rises", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Planning\" data-id=\"175599141\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">blackred</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Both sovereign wealth funds and pension funds deployed less capital into new deals as M&amp;A markets cooled in 2022 and 2023. But only pension funds managed to reverse course in 2024.</p> <p>The aggregate global value of sovereign wealth</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745751-sovereign-funds-pull-back-on-transactions-financial-media-deal-value-rises", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 10:05:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745749", "title": "The Global Growth Engine: 2025 And Beyond", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cog wheels with world on abstract technology background\" data-id=\"2027091478\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"922px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Rasi Bhadramani/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Transcript</h2> <p><strong>Hugo Scott-Gall:</strong> Today, I'm delighted to have with me William Blair's very own Simon Fennell and Olga Bitel back on the show. We are going to discuss our outlook for next year and beyond through the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745749-global-growth-engine-2025-beyond", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 09:40:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745745", "title": "Tutor Perini: Fewer Disputes, More Profits On The Horizon", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tutor Perini headquarters in Sylmar, California, USA.\" data-id=\"1442855367\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Investment thesis</strong></h2> <p>It\u2019s been quite a while since I\u2019ve seen a company tossed and turned by disputes with its customers like Tutor Perini Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TPC\" title=\"Tutor Perini Corporation\">TPC</a></span>) has been for the past few years.</p> <p>In its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/19906235-tutor-perini-reports-third-quarter-2024-results#hasComeFromMpArticle=false\">third-quarter earnings release</a>, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745745-tutor-perini-fewer-disputes-more-profits-on-the-horizon", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 09:25:10", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745742", "title": "Why Veolia's Potential Outweighs Its Risks For Me", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of the Veolia Recycling and Energy Recovery Plant in Leeds\" data-id=\"1435403566\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Teamjackson</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>I recently came across <strong>Veolia Environnement SA (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VEOEY\" title=\"Veolia Environnement SA\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:VEOEY</a>)</strong> after it hit a fresh 52-week low. What caught my attention is the disconnect between its strong \"Buy\" ratings from <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VEOEY/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VEOEY/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\">Wall Street</a> and <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VEOEY/ratings/author-ratings\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VEOEY/ratings/author-ratings\" target=\"_blank\">Seeking Alpha</a>, along with solid </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745742-why-veolias-potential-outweighs-its-risks-for-me-veoef-veoey", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 09:15:38", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745740", "title": "Prologis: Buy The Best At A Bargain", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rubber ducks in a row with one facing backwards\" data-id=\"108359511\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1148px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andy Roberts/OJO Images via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>The Trend Is Your Friend</h2> <p>This idiom reaches far and wide across the investment universe. Generally speaking, hopping on the bandwagon of red hot sectors and chasing the smart money is wise. Looking back at some</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108359511/image_108359511.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745740-prologis-buy-the-best-at-a-bargain", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 09:05:33", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745736", "title": "Palantir: Winning The Race To AGI", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Palantir Technologies headquarters campus exterior view in Silicon Valley. - Palo Alto, California, USA - 2019\" data-id=\"1313497441\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5564px\" height=\"3746px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Vi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-Authored by Noah Cox and Brock Heilig</em></p> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Palantir Technologies (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PLTR\" title=\"Palantir Technologies Inc.\">PLTR</a></span>) shares have beaten the market since the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4734158-palantir-q3-earnings-deep-dive-after-the-election\">last time</a> I wrote on them (November 7th) after the US Presidential election and the most recent earnings</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313497441/image_1313497441.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745736-palantir-winning-the-race-to-agi", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 08:52:32", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745735", "title": "Wix.com: Full Steam Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"video hosting website. movie streaming service. digital photo album.\" data-id=\"861148402\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/861148402/image_861148402.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com